        {
            "id": 6326599,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 高特利集團(MO-US)大跌5.01%，報59.97美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>高特利集團(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MO:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MO\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MO-US</a>)截至台北時間30日03:49股價下跌3.17美元，報59.97美元，跌幅5.01%，成交量14,019,779（股），盤中最高價62.52美元、最低價59.97美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-0.14%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-0.55%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-1.43%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：-0.9%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>高特利集團(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MO:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MO\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MO-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+4.16%</li> <li>近 1 月：+10.45%</li> <li>近 3 月：+0.54%</li> <li>近 6 月：+8.34%</li> <li>今年以來：+10.34%</li></ul></section></main>",
